c: 46
v: 20
t: "On that Day when the disbelievers will be brought before the fire, they will be told: \"You squandered away your good things in your earthly life and you enjoyed them for a while. Today you shall be recompensed with a punishment of humiliation because you behaved with arrogance for which you had no right during your life on earth and because of the transgressions you committed"